#

<span key="9a1b81e70ce146b79fa43caaecd070bd"><span offset-key="9a1b81e70ce146b79fa43caaecd070bd:0">Widgets</span></span>

<span key="19a295dbe4cb4882a9fc1d082f143130"><span offset-key="19a295dbe4cb4882a9fc1d082f143130:0">Widgets define the data type and interface for entry fields. Netlify CMS comes with several built-in widgets. Click the widget names in the sidebar to jump to specific widget details. We’re always adding new widgets, and you can also </span></span><a href="https://www.netlifycms.org/docs/custom-widgets" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="02387eed6d3b4b838c6af3441a7916b2" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="a57ff023efe3487a9be017a3400a54e1"><span data-offset-key="a57ff023efe3487a9be017a3400a54e1:0">create your own</span></span></span></a><span key="3fd2e3748e704da482d283543141e1f7"><span offset-key="3fd2e3748e704da482d283543141e1f7:0">!</span></span>

<span key="2d1165e3ae8c4ec48b47a532512235ca"><span offset-key="2d1165e3ae8c4ec48b47a532512235ca:0">Widgets are specified as collection fields in the Netlify CMS </span>`config.yml`<span offset-key="2d1165e3ae8c4ec48b47a532512235ca:2"> file. Note that </span></span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YAML#Basic_components" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="d891f7ab75814b65a168f9708e9c8b6c" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="757b13e0f223459bbab2ba0dc3e92280"><span data-offset-key="757b13e0f223459bbab2ba0dc3e92280:0">YAML syntax</span></span></span></a><span key="e47419d043dc4e68977fc9914761e1ed"><span offset-key="e47419d043dc4e68977fc9914761e1ed:0"> allows lists and objects to be written in block or inline style, and the code samples below include a mix of both.</span></span>

<span key="ea8f2a8f34a24fd9b45eb5330b9702a1"><span offset-key="ea8f2a8f34a24fd9b45eb5330b9702a1:0">To see working examples of all of the built-in widgets, try making a 'Kitchen Sink' collection item on the </span></span><a href="https://cms-demo.netlify.com" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="aee4f0f832e84dcda7989ef6c218f4b1" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="459d038b5c3849ddb35b9a76b8cf7f00"><span data-offset-key="459d038b5c3849ddb35b9a76b8cf7f00:0">CMS demo site</span></span></span></a><span key="e1880395e7394c4699dd16af2a5d3e0b"><span offset-key="e1880395e7394c4699dd16af2a5d3e0b:0">. (No login required: click the login button and the CMS will open.) You can refer to the demo </span></span><a href="https://github.com/netlify/netlify-cms/blob/master/dev-test/config.yml" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="cdb09598b3c746639b570b3a07937d32" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="f20228deab2148d4a9875ef34afba0e1"><span data-offset-key="f20228deab2148d4a9875ef34afba0e1:0">configuration code</span></span></span></a><span key="508efc2981814a75b1d3dd5530d4268d"><span offset-key="508efc2981814a75b1d3dd5530d4268d:0"> to see how each field was configured.</span></span>

##

<span key="d17ef13f9b46420c925e0f4a584b5cef"><span offset-key="d17ef13f9b46420c925e0f4a584b5cef:0">Common widget options</span></span>

<span key="3f6a749b70c4445381e22c85b5a16974"><span offset-key="3f6a749b70c4445381e22c85b5a16974:0">The following options are available on all fields:</span></span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="87cea70848ba41f9bc97952e2137e501">`required`<span offset-key="87cea70848ba41f9bc97952e2137e501:1">: specify as </span>`false`<span offset-key="87cea70848ba41f9bc97952e2137e501:3"> to make a field optional; defaults to </span>`true`</span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="9cb9dd0560d94698a81e6385182836c0">`hint`<span offset-key="9cb9dd0560d94698a81e6385182836c0:1">: optionally add helper text directly below a widget. Useful for including instructions. Accepts markdown for bold, italic, strikethrough, and links.</span></span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="0f7c8da3a33f44d2ac94df6a1c2d1664">`pattern`<span offset-key="0f7c8da3a33f44d2ac94df6a1c2d1664:1">: add field validation by specifying a list with a </span></span><a href="https://regexr.com" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="29b2e59dac554b4da32bd2c14405d3ff" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="a80dad8e88f84460aa41eefbf8f95d61"><span data-offset-key="a80dad8e88f84460aa41eefbf8f95d61:0">regex pattern</span></span></span></a><span key="1e3894ce716d4a67a5b89decdc5f4576"><span offset-key="1e3894ce716d4a67a5b89decdc5f4576:0"> and an error message; more extensive validation can be achieved with </span></span><a href="https://www.netlifycms.org/docs/custom-widgets/#advanced-field-validation" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="08f5cf2de15141acbd43b917d0ee8b13" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_260-10034_262-10035-240__"><span data-key="017aa7598ef94e79995dfb4a334dfb77"><span data-offset-key="017aa7598ef94e79995dfb4a334dfb77:0">custom widgets</span></span></span></a><span key="aa413640d37f417e80609f93e5858573"><span offset-key="aa413640d37f417e80609f93e5858573:0"><span slate-zero-width="z">​</span></span></span>

  - <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="7d1207e866dd4868a7e994c745aa09b4">**Example:**<span offset-key="7d1207e866dd4868a7e994c745aa09b4:1"> </span>`yaml - label: "Title" name: "title" widget: "string" pattern: ['.{12,}', "Must have at least 12 characters"]`</span>

<span key="27b6c2facac446479a0366d980ebb895"><span offset-key="27b6c2facac446479a0366d980ebb895:0">Boolean</span></span>

<span key="fb5068d1b55a4400bc5873a647e3e045"><span offset-key="fb5068d1b55a4400bc5873a647e3e045:0">The boolean widget translates a toggle switch input to a true/false value.</span></span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="a9c544d66b434398921dcd778338e29d">**Name:**<span offset-key="a9c544d66b434398921dcd778338e29d:1"> </span>`boolean`</span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="350815edf57d43959e3a55beda2c5516">**UI:**<span offset-key="350815edf57d43959e3a55beda2c5516:1"> toggle switch</span></span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="19407087943c4897a28a474a3dfa2290">**Data type:**<span offset-key="19407087943c4897a28a474a3dfa2290:1"> boolean</span></span>

- <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

  <span key="08c8545abfb84173a8fdb918e0abd640">**Options:**</span>

  - <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

    <span key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718">`default`<span offset-key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718:1">: accepts </span>`true`<span offset-key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718:3"> or </span>`false`<span offset-key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718:5">; defaults to </span>`false`<span offset-key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718:7"> when </span>`required`<span offset-key="b33a6dc01a7545daa98e6a9f061c1718:9"> is set to </span>`false`</span>
